This paper deals with sentiment classification of product reviews, which is a common task in natural language processing. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CL (Computation and Language). The paper also involves machine learning techniques, which suggests that it could also belong to cs.LG (Machine Learning). Additionally, the paper involves information retrieval techniques, which could place it in cs.IR (Information Retrieval). The use of state-of-the-art classifiers suggests that it could also belong to cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence). Finally, the paper involves analyzing text data, which could place it in cs.CV (Computer Vision) as well.
